$interpreted: Kittyeyes: We've arrived at our position, right here.
Koll: Aroo.
Kittyeyes: Koll, once our comrades stop the convoy from the front, we'll circle behind and surround the convoy on both sides. Understand?
Koll: Aroo!
Kittyeyes: Our mission is important. No mistakes allowed!
Koll: Arroo!
Kittyeyes: After all, this is a mission specifically assigned to me by Roger.
Koll: Wooo...
Kittyeyes: Koll, Roger assigned me to an important mission. This means he really does trust me, right?
Kittyeyes: Then I must perform my absolute best to not disappoint him.
Kittyeyes: What's the matter...huh, this sound...the footsteps of Kalta Beasts?
Kittyeyes: The convoy arrived early!? Koll, we gotta move, quick!

Roger: Listen, only thing we want is the convoy's cargo.
As long as you behave yourselves and don't cause any trouble, I will not harm you. I promise.
Cowardly Bodyguard: Seems like those bandits didn't realize we're hiding here?
Useless Bodyguard: Let's get outta here. Go get the Kingdom's army to save the people .
Kittyeyes: Huff~ Puff~ I'm out of breath...Where do you guys think you're going?
Roger: Kittyeyes, are you alright?
Kittyeyes: Not a single scratch. Check this out, Roger; I completed the mission you assigned me without a hitch.
Roger: Haha, I knew it was the right decision to entrust you with the mission.
Kittyeyes: Of course it is~
Roger: After all, you're my little sister. I trust you more than anyone else.
Kittyeyes: Oh...I see...
Roger: I'll get everyone to unload the cargo. See you later.
Kittyeyes: ...I don't work so hard just to be seen as your little sister...
